MASH (Modular Analysis and Simulation for Human Health)

MASH is a generic, modular, and extensible modeling framework for the modeling and analysis of mosquito-borne pathogens.

Details

Please refer to http://smitdave.github.io/MASH-Development/index.html for documentation, citations, publications, acknowledgements, and examples. Please refer to https://smitdave.github.io/MASH/index.html for reference and vignettes.
